### Volunteer Matching Helper API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### 1. Admin Login (Get Token)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### Extract Token
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 2. Get All Roles (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. Get All Volunteers (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/volunteers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Get Volunteers (Admin) - Filter by Skill ID (e.g., Skill ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/volunteers?skill_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 5. Get Volunteers (Admin) - Filter by Day of Week
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/volunteers?day_of_week=Saturday
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Public Intake Form (Create Volunteer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/public/volunteers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "volunteer": {
    "first_name": "John",
    "last_name": "Doe",
    "email": "john.doe.new@example.com",
    "phone": "555-0199",
    "availabilities_attributes": [
      {
        "day_of_week": "Saturday",
        "time_of_day": "Morning"
      }
    ],
    "skills_attributes": [
      {
        "name": "Photography"
      },
      {
        "name": "Driving"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 7. AI Match Stub (Admin) - Requires a valid Role ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/roles/1/ai_match
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
